Package hospitalsystem.model

Class MedicalRecord

java.lang.Object
hospitalsystem.model.MedicalRecord
public class MedicalRecord extends Object
Represents a patient's medical record in the Hospital Management System. A medical record contains personal information, blood type, and appointment outcomes.
